- update and date the changelog
- bump the version number in the source file
- tag and push the code
- build the tarball using "make dist"
- upload the tarball to Google Code (http://code.google.com/p/safe-rm/downloads/list)
- announce the release on Freshmeat (http://freshmeat.net/projects/safe-rm/)
- update and upload the Debian package
- add a new post on the safe-rm blog (http://www.safe-rm.org.nz)
